            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>tuna</strong> and add it to a large bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and most of the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) to the bowl</p><p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and give it a good mix up then set aside to absorb – this is your <strong>Thai-style tuna mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2325-Step-3-x400.jpg",
