            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the<strong> carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Peel lengths off the <strong>cucumber</strong> until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Add the <strong>carrot</strong> and <strong>cucumber ribbons </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled carrot & cucumber ribbons</strong></p>",
